      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've seen the doctors. they just give me more pills that dont really work, they just make me feel groggy while the pain still eats at me. it's like there's no real way out of this cycle. sometimes i just sit here and think about how peaceful it would finally be to just... not exist anymore. like, wouldn't that be the only real mercy left? when the pain is just gone forever?",
