      "content": "but its not just a symptom, its just the logic of it. the doctors talk about \"managing\" it like it's something i'm supposed to just live with forever. but there is no \"better\" coming, they've told me that. i'm just tired of fighting a war that i've already lost. it doesn't feel like a crisis, it just feels like... a rational conclusion. if the only way to get peace is to stop being, isn't that just the kindest option?",
